{"tid":1644240,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[長文慎入]其實場運動係咪開始完","createTime":"2019-10-10T13:12:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T14:32:30.000Z","uid":223043,"like":27,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"a55103f2fe3da88a4bbdbd7af4577664b3772257","tid":1644240,"uid":223043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T13:12:27.000Z","msg":"蒙面法一岀， 集會少左，遊行少左，連商場嗌既都少左。就連我個藍c老豆都問做咩呢幾日咁平靜！<br />\n<br />\n今日apm連一層都圍唔哂，得嗰小貓3,4隻。圍得既又唔嗌，搞到好似喺度圍爐取暖咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人係咪已經冇左當初團火，由當初612每個人都對準政權屌林鄭，撤回之後繼續屌狗，到今日每次岀黎都冇左個大主題，好似每個星期六日既抗爭只係日常習慣咁。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>其實政府真係好聰明</strong></span></span><br />\n正確黎講係喺政府背後岀謀獻策嗰個好聰明<br />\n<br />\n[<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>首先<span style=\"color: green;\"></span></strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">政府撤回</span></span></strong>，等我地轉移仇恨去狗狗到，令到運動演變成多區開花，但係人數，抗爭程度都細左。<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">但係</span></span></ins><br />\n香港人都係好聰明，繼續星期六日抗爭示威遊行，甚至規模比撤回前更大<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">第二</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">禁幪面法</span></span></strong>，加上<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">黨鐵不斷做假借機關站，甚至全日唔開</span></span></strong>，借幪面為由，行<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"></span></strong>為實，太家諗下呢個禮拜係有幾早收工。政府此舉令我地喺平日開花既難度更大，因為一般既藍c，街坊真係翻左屋企之後就唔會再岀街，手足俾狗逗既風險就更大。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">第三</span></strong></span><br />\n政府不斷用<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">不實消息</span></strong></span>黎做海外文宣，不斷抹黑手足！令國際戰線風向開始轉向<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>所以我地更加要對準政權，雖然咦家冇可能可以好似612嗰陣咁多人圍政總，但係起碼每個星期都有遊行集會<br />\n<br />\n1. 五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n2. 文宣手足繼續發揮創意，向外國講香港既實際情況<br />\n3. 平日即使乜事都冇既話，都唔好咁早翻屋企，落街買下零食又好，散下步都好，要掩護做緊野既手足</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>更重要既係！<br />\n平日要帶口罩，著黑衫，我地要做到既就係喺條街到一眼望埋去就係黑海，俾所有人知呢場運動仲未完，大家都未被滅聲！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999，第一次覺得場運動頹左，認唔住手<br />\n香港人！反抗！"},{"pid":"6d2d299c8df937c0328fe54353836e9ef8601dbc","tid":1644240,"uid":191271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T13:13:35.000Z","msg":"【突發】英國首相Boris Johnson 回應「五大訴求」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1644236\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1644236</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a238db52ba9425489f04d48c9837e6c44bb4942a","tid":1644240,"uid":223043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a55103f2fe3da88a4bbdbd7af4577664b3772257","tid":1644240,"uid":223043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T13:12:27.000Z","msg":"蒙面法一岀， 集會少左，遊行少左，連商場嗌既都少左。就連我個藍c老豆都問做咩呢幾日咁平靜！<br />\n<br />\n今日apm連一層都圍唔哂，得嗰小貓3,4隻。圍得既又唔嗌，搞到好似喺度圍爐取暖咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人係咪已經冇左當初團火，由當初612每個人都對準政權屌林鄭，撤回之後繼續屌狗，到今