ces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999，第一次覺得場運動頹左，認唔住手<br />\n香港人！反抗！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T13:14:29.000Z","msg":"我個借幪面為由，行<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">宵禁</span></span></strong></span>為實係人河蟹左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f37915c0faf240aa846f16894d745546921f16b1","tid":1644240,"uid":223043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T13:17:03.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"3e1e78572552ef06eb45f00433d5644fc36dc553","tid":1644240,"uid":19260,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T13:17:13.000Z","msg":"個問題係跨區會犧牲仲多人<br />\n上次10月6日就係咁港島拉左勁多人<br />\n<br />\n同意每個星期都要有遊行集會<br />\n但未必要再係港島搞<br />\n多區開花啦<br />\n總之有商場集會就去<br />\n<br />\n勇武記得快閃就真係快閃<br />\n唔好再傻豬豬留係到比人拉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d97a42aaddeeac6c7a302eb8bc8f8c67b4f763b","tid":1644240,"uid":223043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T13:17:20.000Z","msg":"一推"},{"pid":"75012d4eafc5f86fcd7ff45838047d9a31da6505","tid":1644240,"uid":223043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T13:18:14.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"6c55b6acedafee625f7d2dff4d9435be278d4a4a","tid":1644240,"uid":70897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T13:18:16.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"85d8de7b78edb9d2c70851f0b9905223a73ea021","tid":1644240,"uid":142433,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T13:19:27.000Z","msg":"連登仔要休息 出去會比人話送頭"},{"pid":"8f095c3731953aab1eccdabf371e447e492a58f5","tid":1644240,"uid":319181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T13:19:35.000Z","msg":"唔止謝sir，連er er er sir都&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1644080\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1644080</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1043b2dd001f44da87450d5849db0bc843acb8a6","tid":1644240,"uid":137048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T13:20:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"47887840b7e1f610dc4aa5a6f65abe18a252fd5f","tid":1644240,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T13:21:16.000Z","msg":"有啲錢嘅，移民走哂/俾父母送出國留學<br />\n窮嘅，拉撚哂，男嘅跳樓，女嘅跳海"},{"pid":"9d63dfc7e02165168da09263af53e08db12caa7e","tid":1644240,"uid":32672,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T13:21:47.000Z","msg":"多謝班休息撚！"},{"pid":"5f6f3aa0af30a53424c8313bd40c1942165d9532","tid":1644240,"uid":40667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T13:22:08.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5143376e0516fcf252ec58ebd141bb9f4ead029e","tid":1644240,"uid":326076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T13:22:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2b454bf5dfd45acd493ebb10621744371fbe0377","tid":1644240,"uid":142433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T13:23:24.000Z","msg":"一有人叫出去 頭幾個留言就「no sir! 」「sorry sir」<br />\n戇撚鳩"},{"pid":"c968baa53643ab5a665edf2f22fce77aff6a5ad7","tid":1644240,"uid":321977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T13:27:36.000Z","msg":"我都覺，唉<br />\n口罩都唔撚帶，講經咩"},{"pid":"7ae2d652935a2a2fa170c0bd46ca5bc187b081e3","tid":1644240,"uid":289991,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T13:28:39.000Z","msg":"我唔同意。<br />\n<br />\n呢幾個月幾乎個個星期都有活動，其實大家真係攰。不斷重複的遊行，放TG, 開戰。加上拘捕的人數太多，大家真係唔好再送頭。我地而家需要new inspiration and ideas. <br />\n<br />\n我個人而言，抗爭的心和士氣沒減，呢一刻等緊智者再出計。到時一定會全力配合。"},{"pid":"8bd97fccec5f6e1650fb74a8cbb8c60ebe5edce4","tid":1644240,"uid":203755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T13:29:16.000Z","msg":"日日都話休息<br />\n突發改活動(上星期六和理非出晒街得連登仔話改休息日)<br />\n又有班人話等人權法過左先再繼續&hellip;<br />\n團火熄左好難點返著<br />\n有時都要睇返721 805 831 101先點返著自己團火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n加上黨鐵助攻宵禁令出街既意慾減低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c596713f821a429a15cd35e4beedbe1d25add2a","tid":1644240,"uid":324500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T13:31:29.000Z","msg":"年輕人呀! 我P 牌有少少意見，連登好多激情post 成日要衝，但有冇諗過吓吓正面衝突結果損兵折將，只呈一時之快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n抗爭是長久，敵進我退，敵退我進,方才是個不敗哲學。皆因我們是蛋，敵方是高牆。<br />\n踢波90分鐘都冇理由一味攻而唔退守回氣。而家反蒙面法呢個回合就當敵方上風，我地要沉澱下再見機再反撃，其實對敵相方都係揾對方犯錯再追撃&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n希望各兄弟從失意中再伺機反撃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不氣餒!兄弟爬山，共勉之!"},{"pid":"8b346429617cd3d23b5bd8e0210137e1f28e1cec","tid":1644240,"uid":32904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f37915c0faf240aa846f16894d745546921f16b1","tid":1644240,"uid":223043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T13:17:03.000Z","msg":"自推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T13:34:13.000Z","msg":"我都感覺到就完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n10月1大戰完之後就冇左主線<br />\n口罩日都冇咩人帶<br />\n<br />\n721 831 警暴咁多核彈都用唔到咩效果"},{"pid":"4fcba836c86d463e82a3162719c975d22ef18a49","tid":1644240,"uid":136115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T13:43:12.000Z","msg":"跪求大家同我地一齊 繼續出嚟"},{"pid":"7ca5d0afec0f66f96733f7afca9699d0939ef5c8","tid":1644240,"uid":162954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T13:45:18.000Z","msg":"Trump trump都話要黎一次百萬人大遊行"},{"pid":"a1505f935462bec2cbcad34d8eedfd31a43e1e1c","tid":1644240,"uid":40667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T13:47:22.000Z","msg":"百萬人大遊行 多區開花"},{"pid":"e9f8ba7e27b25d42a10dd513e5805447b2847a6e","tid":1644240,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T13:47:59.000Z","msg":"pish"}]}